1: "wget" or "git clone git://github.com/xianglei/phpHiveAdmin.git"

2:. untar it.

3: add this follow to your nginx.conf in your "location ~ .php$ {};"
 area

fastcgi_connect_timeout 36000;
fastcgi_send_timeout 36000;
fastcgi_read_timeout 36000;

4: in php 5.3.9 open $PHP_HOME/etc/php-fpm.conf modify to this:

process_control_timeout = 36000s

and this:

request_terminate_timeout = 36000s

open $PHP_HOME/lib/php.ini modify to this:

max_input_time = 36000

and this:

default_socket_timeout = 36000

5: restart nginx && php-fpm

IMPORTANT:

for localized language using,modify /config.inc.php and /index.php,
 in these files, change "langs/lang_xx.php" to your language set.

for security, modify access_list file change only IP to your IP lists
 for access, an IP addr each line.